<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>You Have a Pending Commission</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .signature {
      color: #D8C1A9;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>You Have a Pending Commission</h1>
    <p>You have a pending commission. Please check the details below:</p>
    <p><strong>Commission Type:</strong> <%= @commission.commission_type.title %></p>
    <p><strong>Price:</strong> PHP<%= (@commission.price) %></p>
    <p><strong>Additional Information:</strong> <%= @commission.description %></p>
    <p><strong>Status:</strong> <%= @commission.stage %></p>
    <p><strong>Buyer Contact Information:</strong> <%= @commission.buyer.user.contact_information.present? ? @commission.buyer.user.contact_information : "No contact information available" %></p>
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out via this email. We are committed to ensuring that you have an exceptional experience. ü§ù</p>
    <p class="signature">Best regards, <br> The Project:CAMAY Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
